SEO.title: BlueX | Better Business Payments for Global Supply Chain Players
SEO.description:
The global b2b trade finance platform for payments and pay-it-later for scaling international trade, amplifying cash flows, and expediting cargo releases.

Improve your business cash flow and get more time to pay with BlueX Pay-it-Later, which offers up to 1 million in funds in around 48 hours. You can use it for all your logistics services and your cargo. Simply sign up online for free and upload your invoice online. Whether your business is growing and needs cash to buy more goods or wants more time for your outstanding invoice, BlueX can help.

Section_7_FAQ_List.title: Why should I use BlueX Pay-it-Later?
Section_7_FAQ_List.content: BlueX pays your vendors on your behalf, so you can get your goods first and pay for them later. We have years of experience in the supply chain, working with the largest ocean carriers and global freight forwarders. There is no application fee or collateral needed; instead, we charge a low handling fee.

Section_7_FAQ_List.title: How does it work?
Section_7_FAQ_List.content: [Sign up](https://portal.bluexpay.com/signup/company_info) is quick and easy! Once approved, BlueX will provide you with a Pay-it-Later limit that you can use for invoices of your cargo, freight and logistics services.

Section_7_FAQ_List.title: How long do I get to pay my invoice?
Section_7_FAQ_List.content: We offer net 30 or 60 day terms. You can select the terms each time you submit an invoice to get paid.

Section_7_FAQ_List.title: How do vendor payments work?
Section_7_FAQ_List.content: We make the payment to your vendor on your behalf by your scheduled payment date via ACH, Fedwire, or SWIFT. It doesn’t cost anything for your vendor to receive payments, and it doesn’t change their billing process.

Section_7_FAQ_List.title: How do I sign up?
Section_7_FAQ_List.content: Sign up takes less than 5 minutes! Please click [here](https://portal.bluexpay.com/signup/company_info) to sign up. Contact us at [sales@bluexpay.com](mailto:sales@bluexpay.com) if you have any questions.
